SIROCCO2
------------------------------------------
This is a library for computing homotopy continuation of a given root of one
dimensional sections of bivariate complex polynomials. The output is a
piecewise linear approximation of the path followed by the root, with the
property that there is a tubular neighborhood, with square transversal section,
that contains the actual path, and there is a three times thicker tubular
neighborhood guaranted to contain no other root of the polynomial. This second
property ensures that the piecewise linear approximation computed from all
roots of a polynomial form a topologically correct deformation of the actual
braid, since the inner tubular neighborhoods cannot intersect.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.2-1
  libgcc1-11.2.0-1
  libmpfr6-4.1.0-2
  libsirocco0-2.1.0-1bl1
  libstdc++6-11.2.0-1
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.37-2
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-11.2.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.2.0-1
  libmpfr-devel-4.1.0-2
  libtool-2.4.6-8
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/miguelmarco/SIROCCO2

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/miguelmarco/SIROCCO2/archive/refs/tags/2.1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack SIROCCO2-2.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./SIROCCO2-2.1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/SIROCCO2-2.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/SIROCCO2-2.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsirocco0-2.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libsirocco-devel-2.1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(SIROCCO2)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/SIROCCO2.README
  /usr/share/doc/SIROCCO2/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/SIROCCO2/README.md

(libsirocco0)
  /usr/bin/cygsirocco-0.dll

(libsirocco-devel)
  /usr/include/sirocco.h
  /usr/lib/libsirocco.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libsirocco.pc

